snippet.title: The Adjudicator - Trailer
snippet.description:
"The Adjudicator" is an interactive video product deduced by real people. It uses the method of film + interactive gameplay to promote the development of the plot. The trend of the plot will be determined by you.
Developer : 水思维
Publisher : BD Games
